6b05846e-00f8-495e-b9bd-04beaf2294c4.title: Note
6b05846e-00f8-495e-b9bd-04beaf2294c4.text: Missing talking to after giving meats

92cd7c2b-d925-40b6-9c2a-ae09c345a087.title: Sanfew
92cd7c2b-d925-40b6-9c2a-ae09c345a087.text: What can I do for you young 'un?

720cf0bc-7885-40ab-9ef4-9ac4b03939e8.title: <player>
720cf0bc-7885-40ab-9ef4-9ac4b03939e8.text: Actually, I don't need to speak to you.

8de2bb0b-dcbe-4e18-a643-f03c1539ec3c.title: Sanfew
8de2bb0b-dcbe-4e18-a643-f03c1539ec3c.text: Well, we all make mistakes sometimes.

8942cbba-4813-4ec5-8e33-39753fc85b79.title: Sanfew
8942cbba-4813-4ec5-8e33-39753fc85b79.text: What can I do for you young 'un?

options.text: 遰 I've been sent to help purify the Varrock stone circle.
Actually, I don't need to speak to you.

dadf3c60-d162-4531-a8fe-fac09f05d0c3.title: <player>
dadf3c60-d162-4531-a8fe-fac09f05d0c3.text: Actually, I don't need to speak to you.

46b75faf-edae-4467-a0f8-0b171e85b5df.title: Sanfew
46b75faf-edae-4467-a0f8-0b171e85b5df.text: Well, we all make mistakes sometimes.

62a12839-5c47-401a-a8a3-20f4fa31e450.title: <player>
62a12839-5c47-401a-a8a3-20f4fa31e450.text:
I've been sent to assist you with the ritual to purify the
Varrockian stone circle.

adadc02c-df83-428f-90c5-6133d5879d17.title: Sanfew
adadc02c-df83-428f-90c5-6133d5879d17.text:
Well, what I'm struggling with right now is the meats
needed for the potion to honour Guthix. I need the raw
meat of four different animals for it, but not just any
old meats will do.

c5595fb3-0776-408c-8f82-fab6c4f74d83.title: Sanfew
c5595fb3-0776-408c-8f82-fab6c4f74d83.text:
Each meat has to be dipped individually into the
Cauldron of Thunder for it to work correctly.

options.text: Where can I find this cauldron?
遰 Ok, I'll do that then.

2ddaaf2e-1eef-48b4-9df3-c5cb0324c80a.title: <player>
2ddaaf2e-1eef-48b4-9df3-c5cb0324c80a.text: Where can I find this cauldron?

b864ab1e-cdc8-44f0-8b7a-058324f940de.title: Sanfew
b864ab1e-cdc8-44f0-8b7a-058324f940de.text:
It is located somewhere in the mysterious underground
halls which are located somewhere in the woods just
South of here. They are too dangerous for me to go
myself however."

9733188b-d2c2-45e4-aa7e-1c321e93937e.title: Sanfew
9733188b-d2c2-45e4-aa7e-1c321e93937e.text:
Did you bring me the required ingredients for the
potion?

36b51f4a-5875-4ba3-b35f-6c5a27e66eff.title: Sanfew
36b51f4a-5875-4ba3-b35f-6c5a27e66eff.text: Well let me know when you do young 'un.

options.text: What was I meant to be doing again?

9d27bfe0-5fce-4dee-ac66-8fab62ad0269.title: Sanfew
9d27bfe0-5fce-4dee-ac66-8fab62ad0269.text:
Trouble with your memory eh young 'un? I need the
raw meats of four different animals that have been
dipped into the Cauldron of Thunder so I can make
my potion to honour Guthix.

ed42b3db-d85c-4389-bb41-434a158f1200.title: <player>
ed42b3db-d85c-4389-bb41-434a158f1200.text: What was I meant to be doing again?

options.text: Where can I find this cauldron?

a4eecd02-f2f9-4b31-ae2f-5a2e7ebc2739.title: <player>
a4eecd02-f2f9-4b31-ae2f-5a2e7ebc2739.text: Where can I find this cauldron?

2ef83896-5a84-4e00-8aad-fc5d4f48c30b.title: Sanfew
2ef83896-5a84-4e00-8aad-fc5d4f48c30b.text:
It is located somewhere in the mysterious underground
halls which are located somewhere in the woods just
South of here. They are too dangerous for me to go
myself however.

8b671acf-5fc9-41c3-b165-eda041c75def.title: Sanfew
8b671acf-5fc9-41c3-b165-eda041c75def.text:
Did you bring me the required ingredients for the
potion?

3ed18cd8-fa99-4248-a4dd-6d50d3a9e29b.title: <player>
3ed18cd8-fa99-4248-a4dd-6d50d3a9e29b.text: Yes, I have all four now!

e0604f14-86de-4686-bfa5-a9ecb997683f.title: Sanfew
e0604f14-86de-4686-bfa5-a9ecb997683f.text:
Thank you so much adventurer! These meats will allow
our potion to honour Guthix to be completed, and bring
one step closer to reclaiming our stone circle!

915ca496-914b-40a0-b1ae-ede447061801.title: Sanfew
915ca496-914b-40a0-b1ae-ede447061801.text:
Now go and talk to Kaqemeex and he will introduce
you to the wonderful world of herblore and potion
making!
